Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:07.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,天空是灰色的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:11.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,城市突然陌生起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:13.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:20.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在妈妈面前 我是不会哭的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:25.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也决定今后绝对不会再哭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:29.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸走了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:33.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈已经把我该流的泪流光了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:38.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在得到的的东西被夺走之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:40.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次感受到名为寂寞的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:43.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是从一开始就不曾拥有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:44.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,连寂寞都不知为何物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直安逸地活在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:49.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:51.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:53.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:57.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你为我的世界染上了色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:01.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 小花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:04.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我找你好久了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:08.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈打电话跟我说你不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:11.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来 跟我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:14.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:21.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,突然为逞强的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感到难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:28.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:31.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个给我温暖港湾的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:34.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又将我一个人抛下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:43.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:48.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘的头发很柔顺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,斜刘海很衬她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:55.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:56.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:58.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:02.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,----------------------OP-----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:56.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:02.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没傻到那地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:08.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但就算跟那家伙说了 她也绝对不会理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说会讨厌我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:19.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然不想被那家伙讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:25.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…也有过真的无法理解的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要针对茜姐 说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦还真是幼稚呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然和那种大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个估计是大学的教授
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那天我哭了一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:06.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:13.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐若无其事的来当我的家庭教师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃蛋糕吗 我买了些来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和昨天一样的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是因为觉得可爱才这样歪头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:32.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人 没有男人的话就活不下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何 我这样想着的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:40.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就觉得茜姐是个脆弱又可怜的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:45.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小麦 沾到奶油了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:55.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 情侣酒店里洗发水的香味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:57.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:03.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:12.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在那之后我不知为何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:17.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自动铅笔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,计算好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:23.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就连肤浅的样子也都是计算好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何更进一步地被她俘获了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好那一口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:49.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是学姐吃醋的表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是换成那家伙的话肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:06.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,眼光太差了去死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:06.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1200)\bord3\frz-90\\b0\fs82.5\t(0,2900,\fs45)\fn@方正卡通简体\c&HB29098&\3c&HF3F3F8&\move(528,535,687.5,515.5,20,2940)}别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:12.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她那种直率的地方 我并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是周六
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我闲着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:28.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你会来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:43.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:49.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来拯救下我的思春期
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:56.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太浪费时间了 去酒店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是想做才叫我出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦 反正我也有责任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:15.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你不用因为责任感之类而和我做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:18.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想是想…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以前都是我主动提出上床的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:43.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你发现了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这下就两清了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:01.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈她没有留宿就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 麦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:10.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:23.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就到暑假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是升学班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:30.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作业好像超多的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:39.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我和麦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前某刻非常地亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:43.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那并非错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:48.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是又变成像这样的陌生人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:51.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,两人在一起的时间变少了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:55.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,变得不太说那些触碰真心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:10:00.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥已经告白了的事情也没跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们相互间隐约察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:05.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此有了越来越多的隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:09.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至开始避免浪费时间而不再去询问对方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:11.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H424242&\bord0}为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:16.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经有小绘就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:18.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只为了填补寂寞的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:22.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦已经不再是必要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不需要他了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:05.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 和其他人做过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:09.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 花火也做过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:11.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂的啊 因为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:20.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了 大概和我想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:26.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为会变得非常的舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:27.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:36.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算觉得痛苦和不情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:46.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:47.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我和麦很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是肮脏的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:01.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,生活总是平平淡淡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:04.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对任何人都是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:06.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,每天过的是否无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全都取决于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,打铃的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:21.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,铃声 课程表 上学时间 放学时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:25.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后 早睡 早起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,时间不被割分成区间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法为人所见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:32.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里 尽是被束缚着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:41.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我最想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:45.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能带我走出这日常的绝对的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:07.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没来我家了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:13.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 好久没来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:16.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞什么啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:20.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才 才不是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:29.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉 对 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:32.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,经常看到呢 这眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:36.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明在胆怯 在惧怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:38.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,仍在正视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:41.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是漂亮的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真想将她蹂躏并玷污得一塌糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:47.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:51.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明知如此 却不能下手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:13:59.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也 真的想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:08.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很爱护很爱护地把她关在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:21.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回复 还没告诉你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:26.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那然后 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:26.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 别让我说出口啊 真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:27.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:29.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:30.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:34.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是还没好好了解过对方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fn@方正细等线_GBK\frz-90\3c&H030304&\b0\pos(1024.001,521.001)}啊啊 今天也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:40.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 总之 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fn@方正细等线_GBK\frz-90\3c&H030304&\b0\pos(1024.001,549.001)}没有找到乐子的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:45.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钟井老师 今晚反正有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:48.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无趣 无趣 无趣 无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜 没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:03.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想他更努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:06.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是在说学生的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,心烦意乱地一不小心就醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:20.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 本来没想到喝成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:25.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 好无聊嘛 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:29.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:32.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 是 我不太能喝 相当地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:40.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然一开始就知道他很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然比想象中还无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:46.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 真的十分讨厌无聊的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还没 告诉我答复
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,答复…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:57.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 和我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:17.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 哇 对不起 不小心说习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,收回前言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:35.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「无聊的今天」 可能会变成「有趣的今天」了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,开关打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还没消的吻痕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:48.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:56.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨 笨蛋 住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:04.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你的吻痕 被谁看到了会很麻烦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:08.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相对的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天做到最后一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:17.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不不 不是违反规则吗 那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:21.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了 歇斯底里 反复无常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,胡言乱语 自我中心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:25.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全无法交往啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:26.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:35.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 宾馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:39.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:45.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了 姑且像是走过场地去看了下夜景
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:49.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我 非常地 喜欢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后结果还是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:57.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,征求意见？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:00.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都到这里了还在征求意见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:04.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 真是的这人哪里好啊 小花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:11.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 C班的安乐冈同学很可爱对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:15.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去和钟井老师关系十分不错的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:18.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花…安乐冈同学她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:23.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,从小就是邻居 像兄妹一样长大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:27.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去有什么特别的关系的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:35.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧 居然在妒忌那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:57.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…好痛好痛不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,变冷了 身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:16.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:28.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 因为也没喜欢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:33.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「那」算什么啊 「那」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:35.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么想做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:52.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要和我真正地交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:01.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:06.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是处女？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:15.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:32.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:37.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:42.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人 为什么就觉得如此的空虚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:50.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想和谁一起睡之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:55.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么会变得脆弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:07.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天 我和钟井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:33.57,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}让我们一起逃离太阳系 在平行线相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:48.63,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如同你我的影子般延伸着 平行线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.10,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}将胆小怯懦归咎于时代的错也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.47,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}无处可归的我 找寻着愿望的归所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:09.35,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}只愿成为你唇边溢出的只言片语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.82,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}让我们一起逃离太阳系 在平行线相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:30.01,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}带上无法实现的希冀 以及毫无底气的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:39.58,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}倘若感情全部流失殆尽 便由我开始描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:50.45,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如今向你我的影子伸出手 平行线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:33.57,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}太陽系を抜け出して　平行線で交わろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:48.63,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}私と君の影のように伸びている　あぁ平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.10,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}勇気がないのは時代のせいにしてしまえばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.47,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}何処にも行けない　願いの居場所を探してた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:09.35,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}君の唇から　こぼれだす　言葉になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.82,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}太陽系を抜け出して　平行線で交わろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:30.01,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}そんな叶わない望みも　不甲斐ない声も引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:39.58,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}感情全部流しきったら　描き始めてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:50.45,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}私と君の影に今手を伸ばす　あぁ平行線
